00:01:55.360 --> 00:02:00.800
[Amit Varma]: the show to get together and propose what I term dream reforms. I have three guests

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:05.360
[Amit Varma]: on the show today, a record, and each of us will propose three dream reforms that we'd

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:11.160
[Amit Varma]: really love to see. And so will I. So that's a total of 12 dream reforms, each of them

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:16.200
[Amit Varma]: proposed by one of us but discussed by all of us. My guests today are Vivek Kaul, Shruti

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:21.840
