00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:26.880
[Amit Varma]: them by the frequency of their appearances on the scene and the unseen. Vivek has appeared

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:31.560
[Amit Varma]: on a whopping 16 episodes of the show. And I'm beginning to think that he and I should

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:36.360
[Amit Varma]: just get a, not get a room but a separate show of our own so others get a chance on

00:02:36.360 --> 00:02:41.040
[Amit Varma]: this one. Watch this space. Shruti meanwhile has appeared on 11 episodes of the scene and

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:45.720
[Amit Varma]: the unseen and was delighted to get an invite in this episode so she could catch up with

00:02:45.720 --> 00:02:51.960
