00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:56.280
[Amit Varma]: just once on the show. But Sachin Tendulkar had played just one test match at the time

00:02:56.280 --> 00:03:01.680
[Amit Varma]: of his second test match and we all know what happened next. Before I begin my ludicrously

