01:23:56.600 --> 01:23:58.280
[Guest 3]: And why is it difficult to change?

01:23:58.280 --> 01:24:02.880
[Guest 3]: Now, take a look at I mean, so this is something I've thought about for a while.

01:24:02.880 --> 01:24:07.580
[Guest 3]: And the example that I like to give is take a look at the ministry or the minister of

01:24:07.580 --> 01:24:08.580
