[Guest 3]: Okay.

01:24:09.580 --> 01:24:25.480
[Guest 3]: Now, if you take Air India out from him, so in the same way, I mean, you know, a lot of

01:24:25.480 --> 01:24:30.680
[Guest 3]: ministries, if you take the PSUs away from them, I mean, they're gone.

01:24:30.680 --> 01:24:35.960
[Guest 3]: I mean, Ministry of Coal, you take Coal India, let's say you don't privatize, let's say you

