[Guest 3]: So unless that changes, so everything, you know, else is a dream.

01:26:01.680 --> 01:26:04.760
[Amit Varma]: Sure, but I mean, everything we're discussing in this episode, if we bring the political

01:26:04.760 --> 01:26:06.520
[Guest 3]: economy into it, it's a khattam.

