02:27:45.040 --> 02:27:51.040
[Guest 1]: And we are an economy running on loan waivers for the last, like, what, 40 plus years, right?

02:27:51.040 --> 02:27:53.160
[Guest 1]: Post Indira Gandhi, 50 years.

02:27:53.160 --> 02:27:57.720
